\SE[2] Ah, I forgot to mention... \!\SE[3] Considering the
burden on Meria-chan, only Laura-chan and I will go
together.

\SE[0] I don't think we'll be able to come back until we're
fully healed. Let's go when we're ready. \SE[1] To Meria-
chan's Dream World.

\SE[5] It's reassuring... Laura-chan. \SE[2] Could you close
your eyes for a moment?

Well then... We will enter inside Meria-chan. I will send
our consciousness...!
\SE[12]Wait for me... Just a little longer...!

It seems to be called a 'life support system.' It appears to
provide the body with necessary nutrients and oxygen.
However, I'm not quite sure about the exact mechanism.

\SE[2]The thing we're looking for is ahead in the Northern
Cave. Please take care of me. \SE[1]
